        "text": "Numbers 13:21",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "), north of Lake Huleh. It is probably the Rehob of ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Judges 1:31",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
