        "text": "Joshua 19:30",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "; and later it belonged to Syria (",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "2Samuel 10:6",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ") The name means “house of spaciousness.” Robinson (",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Bibl. Res. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
