  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Matthew Henry's Concise Commentary",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "17:7-13 Micah thought it was a sign of God's favour to him and his images, that a Levite should come to his door. Thus those who please themselves with their own delusions, if Providence unexpectedly bring any thing to their hands that further them in their evil way, are apt from thence to think that God is pleased with them.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "",
        "children": []
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Barnes' Notes on the Bible",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Rehob (as Dan afterward) is mentioned as the northernmost point of the land of Canaan ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Numbers 13:21",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", and its position is defined with reference to the entering in of Hamath.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "A city - Rather, \"the\" city. They rebuilt Laish, which they had burned down Judges 18:29. ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "A city - Rather, \"the\" city. They rebuilt Laish, which they had burned down ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Judges 18:29",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ". ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
  {
